WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sq

00:00:05.762 --> 00:00:10.062
Puja e sotme eshte e Vishnumaya,

00:00:10.262 --> 00:00:12.762
qe ishte motra e Shri Krishnas,

00:00:16.362 --> 00:00:19.662
s'ishte planifikuar si nje puja

00:00:20.062 --> 00:00:21.562
nderkombetare qe ne bejme.

00:00:22.762 --> 00:00:25.662
Por thone se per dashurine e Zotit

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:33.162
kur te gjithe adhuruesit mblidhen,

00:00:34.362 --> 00:00:37.562
Zoti gjithashtu duhet te thyeje shume rregulla,

00:00:38.362 --> 00:00:44.362
dhe keshtu u pranua te behej kjo puja.

00:00:44.762 --> 00:00:48.762
Mendoj se te pakten duhej bere nje here, ishte ide e mire.

00:00:49.462 --> 00:00:50.962
Prej dashurise suaj

00:00:51.562 --> 00:00:58.062
dhe perkushtimit tuaj u deshirua,

00:00:59.362 --> 00:01:02.862
dhe keshtu kjo puja do te performohet.

00:01:04.762 --> 00:01:06.762
Eshte thjesht spontane

00:01:07.162 --> 00:01:10.862
qe ndodhi qe une te jem ne kete kohe ne Angli,

00:01:11.162 --> 00:01:13.762
sepse nese do te ndodhte ndonjehere kjo puja,

00:01:14.062 --> 00:01:15.662
duhej te ndodhte ne Indi.

00:01:16.662 --> 00:01:21.962
Sepse kjo eshte puja per nje hyjni,

00:01:23.662 --> 00:01:25.062
Vishnumaya,

00:01:26.662 --> 00:01:31.862
fara e se ciles nuk eshte e lehte te mbillet

00:01:33.362 --> 00:01:34.762
ne vendet perendimore.

00:01:37.162 --> 00:01:42.662
Tani i gjithe programimi shakti eshte kryer

00:01:44.262 --> 00:01:48.662
ne nje menyre te tille qe ne kemi Nenen si Shakti sa per fillim,

00:01:51.362 --> 00:01:54.262
Pastaj kemi tre shakti qe dalin prej Saj,

00:01:54.262 --> 00:01:56.962
sic e dini - Mahakali, Mahalakshmi, Mahasaraswati.

00:01:57.662 --> 00:02:02.262
Dhe me pas kemi femije prej tyre:

00:02:04.462 --> 00:02:06.062
motra dhe vellezer.

00:02:06.362 --> 00:02:10.662
Pra para se fuqia

00:02:11.262 --> 00:02:14.262
e asaj qe ne e quajme gruaja ose bashkeshortja te krijohej,

00:02:14.762 --> 00:02:16.962
ishte fuqia e motres qe u krijua.

00:02:17.462 --> 00:02:21.062
Pra, sic e dini qe u linden Brahma, Vishnu, Mahesha

00:02:21.062 --> 00:02:22.762
per keto tre Shakti,

00:02:22.762 --> 00:02:25.062
dhe te gjithe kishin motra.

00:02:25.862 --> 00:02:28.362
Dhe motrat e tyre ishin te martuara

00:02:29.762 --> 00:02:35.262
- si Motra e Vishnus eshte Parvati

00:02:35.662 --> 00:02:38.362
dhe Ajo ishte e martuar me Shiva.

00:02:37.415 --> 00:02:38.873
Nenen e Hershme.

00:02:39.462 --> 00:02:41.362
Eshte shume e rendesishme per tu kuptuar

00:02:41.862 --> 00:02:45.262
qe keto tre lloj fuqish

00:02:45.262 --> 00:02:49.762
gjithmone luajne ne cakra.

00:02:50.162 --> 00:02:52.262
Dhe nese ju i kuptoni keto tre fuqi,

00:02:52.262 --> 00:02:53.662
si ato luajne,

00:02:54.062 --> 00:02:55.362
atehere do te kuptoni

00:02:55.662 --> 00:02:59.262
cila eshte rendesia e Vishnumaya.

00:02:59.662 --> 00:03:04.662
Vishnumaya eshte cilesia e motres ne nje familje.

00:03:05.062 --> 00:03:09.562
Pra femra eshte fuqia.

00:03:10.062 --> 00:03:14.162
dhe mashkulli eshte fuqia kinetike

00:03:15.062 --> 00:03:18.662
qe thekson fuqite

00:03:19.062 --> 00:03:24.462
e ketyre tre fuqive qe e rrethojne ate.

00:03:26.062 --> 00:03:28.762
Pra kur vjen fuqia mashkullore,

00:03:29.062 --> 00:03:31.562
gjithe keto fuqi behen

00:03:33.662 --> 00:03:39.362
bashkepunetore te dobishme ne veprim me ate fuqi.

00:03:40.662 --> 00:03:44.262
Tani fuqia e Vishnumaya eshte shume e rendesishme per t'u kuptuar,

00:03:44.262 --> 00:03:47.662
sepse fuqia e Nenes eshte per te mbrojtur pafajesine tuaj,

00:03:47.662 --> 00:03:49.862
sepse kjo eshte gjeja me e rendesishme.

00:03:49.862 --> 00:03:53.162
Fuqia e Nenes eshte per te mbrojtur pafajesine tuaj.

00:03:53.662 --> 00:03:58.862
Tani, fuqia e Vishnumayas eshte per te mbrojtur dliresine tuaj.

00:04:00.862 --> 00:04:04.462
Ndonjehere ju s'e kuptoni cfare eshte dliresia

00:04:04.662 --> 00:04:06.962
dhe cfare eshte pafajesia.

00:04:07.662 --> 00:04:11.762
Pafajesia eshte nje fuqi e cila nuk eshte e aktivizuar.

00:04:11.962 --> 00:04:14.462
Sic kemi elektricitetin ne shtepine tone,

00:04:15.162 --> 00:04:19.362
elektreciteti ekziston si pafajesia qe gjendet brenda nesh;

00:04:19.762 --> 00:04:25.862
por miratimi (dekretimi) i saj eshte bere permes dliresise.

00:04:26.362 --> 00:04:27.862
Nje person mund te thote,

00:04:27.862 --> 00:04:31.262
"E bera shume pafajesisht"- jo s'mundet.

00:04:31.762 --> 00:04:34.262
Sepse cfaredo te beni nese eshte e pafajshme,

00:04:34.562 --> 00:04:37.162
s'mund te jete e demshme per karakterin tuaj,

00:04:37.562 --> 00:04:41.762
per pafajesine tuaj ose per drejtesine tuaj.

00:04:42.262 --> 00:04:43.862
Pra keta njerez qe thone keshtu,

00:04:43.862 --> 00:04:46.462
qe "E bera pafajesisht" e kane gabim,

00:04:47.062 --> 00:04:50.762
sepse nese ben ndonje gje pafajesisht ajo shnderrohet ne dliresi.

00:04:51.662 --> 00:04:55.662
Pra kur pafajesia eshte e praktikuar shnderrohet ne dliresi.

00:04:56.462 --> 00:04:59.962
Ju duhet te keni respekt per dliresine tuaj.

00:05:00.962 --> 00:05:04.362
Dliresia eshte ajo qe eshte fuqia e Vishnumaya brenda nesh,

00:05:04.362 --> 00:05:07.162
fuqia e Gauri, eshte virgjeri e paster.

00:05:07.162 --> 00:05:08.862
Ajo nuk martohet.

00:05:10.462 --> 00:05:12.762
Sic e dini qe kur Vishnumaya u krijua,

00:05:13.062 --> 00:05:16.962
sapo pas lindjes se Saj Ajo u vra nga Kamsa.

00:05:18.662 --> 00:05:23.362
Tani per te kuptuar rendesine e dliresie brenda nesh,

00:05:23.862 --> 00:05:26.862
ne duhet te dime qe dliresia eshte themeli

00:05:27.162 --> 00:05:28.762
i te gjithe dharmave.

00:05:29.162 --> 00:05:31.562
Vetem dhe derisa te keni sensin e dliresise

00:05:31.862 --> 00:05:33.362
ju s'mund te keni dharma.

00:05:33.862 --> 00:05:36.962
Dharma eshte e pamundur sepse ajo eshte themeli.

00:05:37.262 --> 00:05:39.562
Do te jete nje shtepi e kartave;

00:05:39.862 --> 00:05:43.462
nese nuk keni themelin e dliresise

00:05:43.762 --> 00:05:46.762
ajo thjesht do te rrezohet.

00:05:47.562 --> 00:05:50.262
Pra dliresia eshte nje shume shume e rendesishme

00:05:50.562 --> 00:05:52.862
e qe ka qene e sfiduar gjate ne Perendim,

00:05:52.862 --> 00:05:55.162
dhe prandaj po them qe eshte e veshtire

00:05:55.162 --> 00:05:57.562
per te mbjelle faren e dliresise ne kete vend.

00:05:57.762 --> 00:05:59.062
Dhe kjo duhet te ndodhe,

00:05:59.262 --> 00:06:02.362
mendoj duhet te kete nje plan hyjnor,

00:06:02.362 --> 00:06:05.862
qe po ndodh qe kjo puja e madhe

00:06:05.862 --> 00:06:07.062
duhej te jepej ketu.

00:06:07.262 --> 00:06:08.862
Nuk eshte nje puja e lehte per t'u bere

00:06:08.862 --> 00:06:11.162
- eshte per t'u bere nga njerez qe jane te pafajshem,

00:06:11.662 --> 00:06:14.662
per t'u bere nga njerez qe kane ndjekur nje jete shume religjioze;

00:06:14.862 --> 00:06:16.362
ata te cilet kane qene shume te dliret,

00:06:16.662 --> 00:06:18.362
qe e kane respektuar dliresine e tyre.

00:06:18.362 --> 00:06:19.862
Por tani meqe ju jeni shenjtore,

00:06:20.062 --> 00:06:24.162
cdo gje para jush eshte e paster dhe e mire,

00:06:24.162 --> 00:06:27.362
sepse tani ju keni ndjekur nje jete shenjtori.

00:06:27.362 --> 00:06:31.362
Prandaj dliresia eshte zgjuar brenda jush,

00:06:31.362 --> 00:06:35.162
dhe dliresia punon tek ju si Gauri, si kundalini juaj.

00:06:35.662 --> 00:06:40.662
Pra nese vini ne thelbin e jetes religjioze,

00:06:40.962 --> 00:06:45.062
e jetes se drejte, e jetes Sahaja Yoga, eshte dliresi.

00:06:47.462 --> 00:06:49.062
Nuk mund ta tjetersosh ate.

00:06:49.862 --> 00:06:53.362
Tani kjo dliresi ju jep juve maryadas,

00:06:53.662 --> 00:06:54.962
do te thote ju cakton kufijte.

00:07:00.662 --> 00:07:02.162
(i drejtohet dikujt ne publik- Pse jeni ulur ketu?

00:07:02.162 --> 00:07:04.162
Shkoni me tej, eshte me mire te jeni ne balle.

00:07:04.162 --> 00:07:06.062
Kjo eshte - ju nuk jeni duke bere puja.

00:07:06.262 --> 00:07:08.162
Nese jeni duke bere puja, atehere uluni ketu.

00:07:08.162 --> 00:07:09.962
Perndryshe, me mire uluni.

00:07:09.962 --> 00:07:11.762
Me mire t'i merrni vibrimet e Mia atje,

00:07:11.762 --> 00:07:14.262
ne balle. Ketu, ejani.)

00:07:16.762 --> 00:07:22.762
Pra dliresia eshte ajo qe ju jep maryadas,

00:07:23.062 --> 00:07:24.662
ju jep kufij.

00:07:24.962 --> 00:07:26.662
Si ju jep kufij?

00:07:27.362 --> 00:07:31.162
Si, ne qiell ka vetetime.

00:07:31.862 --> 00:07:35.362
Kur dy rete,

00:07:35.862 --> 00:07:37.862
qe mund te themi jane si Sahaja yogis,

00:07:38.162 --> 00:07:42.362
dalin nga deti

00:07:43.262 --> 00:07:44.162
dhe kane uje te paster

00:07:52.262 --> 00:07:54.862
atje ne, keto re,

00:07:55.162 --> 00:07:57.762
dhe ato duhet ta derdhin;

00:07:59.062 --> 00:08:03.162
kur afrohen se bashku

00:08:03.862 --> 00:08:06.462
dhe kapercejne limitet e egos se tyre,

00:08:06.462 --> 00:08:10.662
ose luftojne me njera tjetren apo ne nje menyre perplasen,

00:08:11.062 --> 00:08:14.562
eshte, aty ka dliresi,

00:08:14.762 --> 00:08:17.062
ne kete vetetime  qe bie.

00:08:17.462 --> 00:08:21.262
Kjo drite e cila te thote qe

00:08:21.262 --> 00:08:24.562
"E ke gabim. Pse je duke luftuar nder vete?

00:08:24.762 --> 00:08:27.062
Pse jeni duke kaluar egon e njeri-tjetrit?"

00:08:27.262 --> 00:08:28.862
Kjo eshte puna e motres.

00:08:29.162 --> 00:08:31.362
Dje kemi patur shume motra.

00:08:31.662 --> 00:08:34.262
Tani detyra e motres nuk eshte te mbaje anen,

00:08:34.862 --> 00:08:37.562
por per te treguar nese i kalon kufijte e tu

00:08:37.762 --> 00:08:39.062
te vellazerise,

00:08:39.362 --> 00:08:42.162
atehere do te kete nje vetetime(drite).

00:08:42.862 --> 00:08:45.962
Tani kjo fuqi e vetetimes

00:08:46.662 --> 00:08:50.062
eshte pjese e fuqise se Shri Krishna

00:08:50.362 --> 00:08:52.662
te cilen Ai e nxorri nga Vetja e Tij.

00:08:53.662 --> 00:08:56.562
Prandaj Ai u be kaq i embel,

00:08:58.362 --> 00:09:01.062
misherim i bute (ndjeshem).

00:09:01.262 --> 00:09:02.262
Ai e nxorri.

00:09:02.262 --> 00:09:04.062
Ai tha, "Tani ti je bere motra Ime,

00:09:04.062 --> 00:09:08.762
dhe sa here qe ata sillen keq me ty ben mire ta perdoresh.

00:09:09.062 --> 00:09:13.862
Keshtu Shri Krishna u be kaq i sjellshem dhe shume,

00:09:14.262 --> 00:09:17.462
sic e quajne misherim romantik;

00:09:18.462 --> 00:09:21.062
sepse Ai nxorri vecmas pjesen moterore

00:09:21.662 --> 00:09:22.862
dhe e vuri ne pune.

00:09:22.862 --> 00:09:25.562
Por ajo ishte gjithmone me Te

00:09:25.562 --> 00:09:26.762
dhe Ajo punoi me Te;

00:09:27.062 --> 00:09:28.862
sepse ne familje motra

00:09:29.162 --> 00:09:31.562
duhet te kuptoje te mos zihet me vellezerit,

00:09:31.962 --> 00:09:33.662
se duhet te kujdeset per ta,

00:09:33.962 --> 00:09:36.462
qe ata te mos sfidohen (kundershtohen) nga te tjeret,

00:09:36.462 --> 00:09:38.762
pra ajo u jep atyre maryadas

00:09:38.762 --> 00:09:42.862
sa larg te shkojne - sa larg te shkojne.

00:09:42.862 --> 00:09:44.862
Tani eshte shume e rendesishme,

00:09:45.062 --> 00:09:48.462
shume, shume e rendesishme per te gjithe ne te kuptojme

00:09:49.062 --> 00:09:53.462
qe Frojdi dhe gjithe njerezit e paarsyeshem

00:09:53.762 --> 00:10:00.462
nxorren teorite per te sfiduar Vishnumaya,

00:10:01.962 --> 00:10:08.962
qe ne ke te kemi gjithe keto lloje qesharake marrdheniesh,

00:10:08.962 --> 00:10:11.362
e cila eshte e pamundur,

00:10:11.762 --> 00:10:12.962
eshte dicka e gabuar.

00:10:13.162 --> 00:10:16.562
Tani nese ka nje marrdhenie te tille

00:10:17.662 --> 00:10:21.162
midis vellait dhe motres,

00:10:21.662 --> 00:10:25.862
familja vuan per shtate breza

00:10:26.162 --> 00:10:29.262
nga semundje te tmerrshme - shtate brezash.

00:10:32.762 --> 00:10:36.562
Por nese ka nje tjeter marrdhenie te stilit Frojd,

00:10:36.562 --> 00:10:40.962
atehere familjes i duhet te vuaje per katermbedhjete breza.

00:10:42.162 --> 00:10:46.562
Pra forcat kufizuese te Vishnumaya jane te tilla

00:10:46.762 --> 00:10:50.462
qe egoja juaj eshte e kontrolluar, superegoja juaj eshte e kontrolluar,

00:10:51.062 --> 00:10:53.162
familja juaj eshte e kontrolluar.

00:10:53.462 --> 00:10:55.562
Cdokush eshte nen kontroll,

00:10:55.762 --> 00:11:00.362
nen drejtimin e kesaj fuqie te paster te Vishnumaya

00:11:01.062 --> 00:11:03.562
qe ndodhet brenda secilit prej nesh.

00:11:04.962 --> 00:11:07.062
Dhe pjesa me e trishtueshme eshte qe

00:11:07.062 --> 00:11:08.762
ne te gjitha vendet Perendimore

00:11:08.762 --> 00:11:12.362
Vishnumaya eshte e semure, absolutisht e semure.

00:11:12.862 --> 00:11:14.962
Dua te them, madje kam humbur edhe Degjimin,

00:11:15.162 --> 00:11:17.362
ka ardhur deri ne kete pike,

00:11:17.762 --> 00:11:18.962
ne anen e majte,

00:11:18.962 --> 00:11:24.362
sepse ndjenja e dliresise mungon teresisht.

00:11:25.762 --> 00:11:27.762
Tani duhet t'i harrojme njerezit

00:11:28.062 --> 00:11:31.862
qe nuk kane fare arsye, tani ne jemi Sahaja yogis.

00:11:32.262 --> 00:11:35.162
Pra te vijme ne piken e duhur, ne duhet te themi qe,

00:11:35.462 --> 00:11:39.562
akoma shume njerez kane mbetur me ide qesharake,

00:11:39.862 --> 00:11:42.862
si "Kam marrdhenie  te mire me ate zoteri"

00:11:43.262 --> 00:11:45.862
ose "Jam shume miqesore me kete apo ate zoteri"

00:11:46.062 --> 00:11:47.062
dhe gjithe keto.

00:11:47.062 --> 00:11:48.962
Pra nuk eshte nje maryada.

00:11:49.762 --> 00:11:55.362
Ju s'mund te keni miqesi me - ndermjet nje burri dhe gruaje,

00:11:55.362 --> 00:11:59.062
s'mundeni, eshte absurde absolutisht.

00:11:59.062 --> 00:12:01.262
Ne Perendim e gjithe kultura eshte qesharake;

00:12:01.262 --> 00:12:03.162
sepse nese shkon ne nje darke

00:12:03.162 --> 00:12:05.062
supozohet te uleni me burrin e dikujt

00:12:05.362 --> 00:12:07.362
ne te dyja anet - e tmerrshme!

00:12:08.162 --> 00:12:11.062
Por ne Lindje, nuk behet,

00:12:12.362 --> 00:12:15.362
sepse Vishnumaya eshte kunder ketyre gjerave.

00:12:15.662 --> 00:12:19.162
Ajo do shohe qe gra e burra ulen se bashku.

00:12:21.362 --> 00:12:24.362
Tani ketu, ju e dini qe pjesa e dliresise

00:12:24.762 --> 00:12:25.962
mungon kaq shume

00:12:25.962 --> 00:12:28.062
sa Vishudhet tuaja te majta po kapen (kane ngerce).

00:12:28.462 --> 00:12:31.162
Dhe kur flas rreth tij, kap edhe me shume.

00:12:32.362 --> 00:12:33.962
Tani kur ju thoni nuk jam fajtor,

00:12:33.962 --> 00:12:36.962
ju ne fakt po e pranoni ndaj Vishnumayas,

00:12:37.162 --> 00:12:38.162
ndaj motres suaj,

00:12:38.462 --> 00:12:41.762
duke i thene "Une nuk jam fajtor."

00:12:41.762 --> 00:12:44.962
Por Ajo nuk pelqen te kete faj mbi ju.

00:12:44.962 --> 00:12:47.362
Gruas mund t'i pelqeje qe ju te keni faj

00:12:47.362 --> 00:12:49.462
Asaj mund t'i pelqeje qe ju  ta keni fajin,

00:12:49.762 --> 00:12:52.062
sepse mendon qe po i sfidohet fuqia

00:12:52.362 --> 00:12:56.062
dhe qe ka dike qe eshte kundershtari i saj.

00:12:56.362 --> 00:12:59.962
Por jo Vishnumaya, jo;

00:12:59.962 --> 00:13:02.762
motra nuk e thote kete.

00:13:03.062 --> 00:13:06.862
Por nje vella e moter nuk jane kurre miq.

00:13:07.862 --> 00:13:09.862
Tani jemi ulur grup ketu.

00:13:09.862 --> 00:13:14.162
Keshtu, ne cdo grup ka nje moter e vella,

00:13:14.662 --> 00:13:17.862
ata e dine qe jane (ekzistojne) si vellezer e motra

00:13:18.162 --> 00:13:19.962
por ata nuk kapen pas nje personi,

00:13:19.962 --> 00:13:21.362
ata nuk i flasin ndonje personi,

00:13:21.362 --> 00:13:24.362
ata s'behen miqesore me ate moter.

00:13:24.862 --> 00:13:28.562
Si dikur ne patem nje fat te madh me keta te Krishtere,

00:13:28.762 --> 00:13:31.162
Kujtoj qe mund te kem patur te pakten

00:13:31.462 --> 00:13:35.562
tridhjete kusherira dhe kater, pese vellezer ne ate kohe.

00:13:36.662 --> 00:13:38.662
Dhe shkuam ne ate ngjarje,

00:13:38.662 --> 00:13:40.262
dhe midis indianeve te krishtere

00:13:40.562 --> 00:13:44.662
ne kemi te Krishtere prej gjithe llojeve te shtresave.

00:13:44.962 --> 00:13:49.162
Keshtu atje ishin disa vagabonde,

00:13:49.162 --> 00:13:51.662
ato hodhen ca fjale rreth nesh,

00:13:51.862 --> 00:13:53.662
ne motrave, kuptoni.

00:13:54.762 --> 00:13:56.362
Ne s'e dinim qe kishim kaq shume kusherinj.

00:13:56.762 --> 00:13:59.862
Ata kercyen perpjete, si me suste (jack-in-the-box lloj lodre)

00:14:00.162 --> 00:14:04.162
i nxorren te gjithe e nisen t'i rrihnin ata djem.

00:14:04.362 --> 00:14:06.862
Atehere e kuptuam se sa shume kusherinj kishim.

00:14:06.862 --> 00:14:08.362
Ndryshe nuk do ta dinim kurre;

00:14:08.362 --> 00:14:10.862
ata ishin diku, ne s'u folem shume atyre,

00:14:10.862 --> 00:14:13.162
po flisnim me njera-tjetren, miqve tane,

00:14:13.162 --> 00:14:14.962
vajza qe flisnin me njera-tjetren.

00:14:14.962 --> 00:14:17.062
Papritur kuptuam sa shume kusherinj kishim

00:14:17.062 --> 00:14:19.762
dhe sa vellezer. Ishte mjaft e papritur

00:14:20.062 --> 00:14:22.162
qe ne te kishim kaq shume kusherinj atje

00:14:22.462 --> 00:14:23.262
dhe ne s'e dinim.

00:14:23.262 --> 00:14:26.062
Menjehere ata u hodhen ne mbrojtje

00:14:26.462 --> 00:14:28.662
te dliresise se motres se tyre,

00:14:28.662 --> 00:14:31.762
sepse ajo eshte baza e dliresise se tyre.

00:14:33.162 --> 00:14:37.662
Por normalisht ju nuk i flisni shume vellait,

00:14:38.162 --> 00:14:41.662
as vellai nuk ju flet ju shume,

00:14:42.062 --> 00:14:43.162
ju nuk beheni miqesore.

00:14:43.162 --> 00:14:46.562
Por ne kohen e veshtiresive, ne kohen e maryadas,

00:14:46.762 --> 00:14:51.862
ne kohen e te konsultuarit per dicka

00:14:52.062 --> 00:14:54.762
qe eshte e shtrenjte ne familje, vjen motra.

00:14:55.562 --> 00:14:57.362
Kohet e fundit vellaim Im, me i vogel,

00:14:57.362 --> 00:14:58.362
Me shkroi nje leter

00:14:58.362 --> 00:15:00.362
sepse kishte nje problem ne familje.

00:15:00.662 --> 00:15:04.762
Tani nena Ime s'eshte atje, dhe normal qe nje moter eshte me mire

00:15:05.062 --> 00:15:09.662
sepse ajo eshte me lehte e gatshme ndaj teje se mamaja.

00:15:09.662 --> 00:15:11.362
Nena eshte kaq e zene me te gjithe familjen,

00:15:11.362 --> 00:15:12.962
gjithe punen, ju e dini cfare ben.

00:15:12.962 --> 00:15:16.162
Keshtu qe ndjenja moterore eshte shume e rendesishme.

00:15:16.362 --> 00:15:20.762
Tani vetem mendoni qe Vishuddhi jone i majte eshte shume keq.

00:15:26.662 --> 00:15:28.262
Sigurisht qe eshte,

00:15:28.462 --> 00:15:30.662
sepse nuk jemi kujdesur kurre per dliresine tone,

00:15:30.862 --> 00:15:33.462
nuk e kemi respektuar dliresine tone.

00:15:33.962 --> 00:15:35.962
Ne Indi nuk ndodh keshtu.

00:15:36.262 --> 00:15:40.762
Gra dhe burra e respektojne shume dliresine e tyre.

00:15:41.162 --> 00:15:43.862
Dhe pyeta disa djem qe kishin shkuar jashte,

00:15:44.162 --> 00:15:46.562
thane qe "Pavaresisht se ishim duke gabuar

00:15:46.562 --> 00:15:49.362
ne ato qe po benim, gjithe kohes ne e dinim disi

00:15:49.762 --> 00:15:51.162
qe po gabonim."

00:15:51.162 --> 00:15:52.162
I them, "Si keshtu?"

00:15:52.162 --> 00:15:55.162
Ai thote, "Ka dicka si marrdhenie me motren."

00:15:58.362 --> 00:16:01.862
Por mund te them tani qe burrat Indiane jane bere

00:16:01.862 --> 00:16:03.362
tamam si ju,

00:16:03.562 --> 00:16:06.662
dhe e kane humbur fuqine e tyre per te mbajtur dliresine e tyre.

00:16:06.962 --> 00:16:09.462
Burrat duhet ta ruajne dliresine e tyre,

00:16:10.062 --> 00:16:14.362
sepse ata mendojne se nuk i detyrohen asgje dliresise.

00:16:14.962 --> 00:16:21.462
Dhe nese thelbi i ekzistences suaj shpirterore

00:16:21.862 --> 00:16:24.662
nuk ekziston, ju do humbisni ne kohe.

00:16:26.162 --> 00:16:28.062
Prandaj e kam thene shume here qe

00:16:28.062 --> 00:16:32.162
vijeni vemendjen tek Nena Toke, gjelberim.

00:16:32.562 --> 00:16:33.762
Gjelberimi eshte ngjyra,

00:16:33.762 --> 00:16:35.862
nese e vini vemendjen tek ajo

00:16:36.162 --> 00:16:39.962
me pas do te shpetoheni

00:16:40.462 --> 00:16:44.162
nga keto gabime te shkeljes se kurores

00:16:44.162 --> 00:16:45.862
gjithe kohes,

00:16:46.662 --> 00:16:48.162
shikoni motrat e te tjereve,

00:16:48.462 --> 00:16:51.362
grate e te tjereve, vajzat e te tjereve.

00:16:52.662 --> 00:16:53.862
Pra marrdhenia

00:16:53.862 --> 00:16:56.562
qe po shprehet tani, sic e dini,

00:16:56.562 --> 00:16:57.362
eshte e nje vajze,

00:17:02.062 --> 00:17:05.762
e nje motre dhe e nje nene,

00:17:06.162 --> 00:17:09.862
qe eshte nje marrdhenie shume shume e paster.

00:17:11.762 --> 00:17:16.262
Kaq shume sa tani, supozojme qe po e perdorni trurin shume,

00:17:16.562 --> 00:17:19.662
atehere pse ju kap ngerci ne zemer - e keni menduar kete?

00:17:19.862 --> 00:17:24.762
Pse ju kap zemra kur perdorni kaq shume anen tuaj te djathte?

00:17:29.862 --> 00:17:33.162
Cili eshte shkaku i ngercit te zemres suaj?

00:17:33.462 --> 00:17:35.962
Duhet te kuptoni kete, eshte e njejta gje.

00:17:36.662 --> 00:17:42.562
Marrdhenia e te themi e Shiva ndaj Vishnus eshte ne dy menyra.

00:17:43.862 --> 00:17:49.862
Se pari Vishnu - grua,motra. Ai ishte martuar.

00:17:51.762 --> 00:17:52.762
Mire?

00:17:52.962 --> 00:17:56.562
Pastaj kush eshte motra e Shivas?

00:17:57.762 --> 00:18:00.262
Motra e Shivas eshte Saraswati.

00:18:00.662 --> 00:18:03.862
Nese punon shume tek Saraswati, zemra ka ngerc.

00:18:04.362 --> 00:18:05.762
Ajo ka maryadas.

00:18:09.962 --> 00:18:12.362
Keshtu zune vend martesat e brendshme,

00:18:12.662 --> 00:18:14.662
prej se ciles marrdhenia e motres

00:18:14.862 --> 00:18:19.962
ka funksionuar per te mbajtur maryadat e cakrave tuaja.

00:18:21.262 --> 00:18:22.562
Nese e kalon kete,

00:18:22.762 --> 00:18:24.662
ju papritur shkoni ne te majte ose ne te djathte

00:18:24.662 --> 00:18:27.362
sepse keni kaluar maryadat e tyre.

00:18:28.762 --> 00:18:31.462
Tani kjo marrdhenie moterore ka ekzistuar

00:18:31.762 --> 00:18:34.662
edhe ne misherime te tjera;

00:18:34.662 --> 00:18:36.562
si Muhamedi

00:18:37.162 --> 00:18:39.462
pati nje marrdhenie moterore

00:18:40.362 --> 00:18:47.162
me - ne fakt duhet ta themi kete

00:18:47.662 --> 00:18:50.362
Motra e tij eshte gruaja e Aliut,

00:18:50.362 --> 00:18:53.762
por Ajo i lindi atij si nje vajze.

00:18:55.062 --> 00:18:59.662
Pra mund te lindin si vajze ose si moter.

00:19:00.162 --> 00:19:03.262
Ajo u lind si motra e Nanakes, Nanaki.

00:19:04.662 --> 00:19:08.062
Ajo u lind si vajza e Muhamedit.

00:19:08.262 --> 00:19:14.162
Pra mund te jete misherimi i nje motre

00:19:15.362 --> 00:19:19.362
ose i nje vajze.

00:19:19.762 --> 00:19:25.962
Por vajza dhe motra jane te pafajshme, dliresi e paster.

00:19:27.462 --> 00:19:30.162
Tani mendoni kete, qe keta njerez

00:19:30.162 --> 00:19:36.762
te cilet s'mund te kuptojne rendesine e dliresise,

00:19:37.362 --> 00:19:42.162
si mund te flasin per ligje cfaredoqofte?

00:19:45.062 --> 00:19:48.162
- sepse "ligje" do te thote maryadas,

00:19:49.462 --> 00:19:53.762
dhe merr kuptimin e duhur

00:19:54.762 --> 00:19:57.262
nepermjet fuqise se Vishnumaya.

00:19:58.462 --> 00:20:02.662
Tani ju mund te thoni qe te mos vjedhesh gjene e tjetrit,

00:20:05.262 --> 00:20:10.162
eshte edhe e padrejte, i perket dikujt tjeter.

00:20:10.762 --> 00:20:12.762
Por kush do iu a thote juve?

00:20:13.162 --> 00:20:16.362
Kush eshte ai qe do ju thote qe kjo eshte gabim?

00:20:16.362 --> 00:20:18.662
Sigurisht, ka police, por

00:20:18.862 --> 00:20:20.362
kush e ka thene?

00:20:20.762 --> 00:20:22.162
Ligjberesit.

00:20:22.962 --> 00:20:26.362
Ajo pjese e te pandergjegjshmes qe ka luajtur eshte Vishnumaya;

00:20:27.162 --> 00:20:30.762
sepse sapo ju vidhni dicka ndiheni fajtore.

00:20:32.462 --> 00:20:35.362
Edhe ne ligj eshte perdorur fjala "fajtor".

00:20:35.962 --> 00:20:40.562
Dhe faji vjen nga ana e majte, eshte Vishnumaya.

00:20:44.962 --> 00:20:49.062
Pra sa e rendesishme eshte te kemi kuptimin (sensin) e dliresise.

00:20:49.762 --> 00:20:51.762
Por ne jemi njerez shume te ndare (percare),

00:20:51.762 --> 00:20:54.762
ne ata qe kane dliresi morale

00:20:54.762 --> 00:20:57.162
dhe ne ata qe mund te mos kene dliresi materiale.

00:20:58.462 --> 00:21:00.862
Ata qe kane dliresi materiale

00:21:01.062 --> 00:21:03.362
mund te mos kene dliresi morale.

00:21:05.262 --> 00:21:07.162
E para vjen dliresia Morale

00:21:07.162 --> 00:21:08.562
kjo eshte shume e rendesishme,

00:21:08.562 --> 00:21:09.962
sepse eshte e lindur.

00:21:10.262 --> 00:21:18.562
Dhe nese dliresia juaj morale eshte ushqyer persosmerisht,

00:21:19.262 --> 00:21:24.762
atehere automatikisht vjen dliresia materiale.

00:21:25.562 --> 00:21:27.362
Por efekti eshte i njejte.

00:21:27.862 --> 00:21:31.862
Nese beni para duke mashtruar ne Sahaja Yoga

00:21:32.262 --> 00:21:34.262
ose nese mashtroni moralisht,

00:21:34.262 --> 00:21:35.962
do te kape Vishuddhi i majte,

00:21:36.262 --> 00:21:40.162
dhe i gjithe problemi do te filloje me Vishuddhin e majte.

00:21:40.662 --> 00:21:44.162
Tani te supozojme qe dikush provon te mashtroje ne Sahaja Yoga,

00:21:44.462 --> 00:21:47.062
do te marre parate e  Sahaja Yoga

00:21:47.362 --> 00:21:48.262
ose dicka te tille.

00:21:48.562 --> 00:21:51.762
Menjehere do te kete ngerce ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:21:52.162 --> 00:21:54.762
Sapo te kapet Vishuddhi i majte

00:21:55.362 --> 00:21:57.362
ai do te filloje te sillet ne nje menyre qesharake,

00:21:57.662 --> 00:21:58.962
do te tregohet i gjithe ngerci,

00:21:59.362 --> 00:22:01.362
Edhe nese do te behesh imoral

00:22:01.362 --> 00:22:03.462
do te kapet Vishuddhi i majte.

00:22:03.762 --> 00:22:07.862
Tani e gjithe pjesa e fajit vjen nga ketu.

00:22:08.762 --> 00:22:12.562
Mekat ndaj Nenes mund te jete gjithashtu edhe nje fyerje,

00:22:12.762 --> 00:22:14.862
ne cfaredo pergjigje ndaj Nenes.

00:22:15.162 --> 00:22:18.762
Kam pare shume njerez qe e kane zakon te thone,

00:22:19.262 --> 00:22:20.262
"Jo, Nene."

00:22:20.662 --> 00:22:23.362
S'duhet te thuhet kurre"Jo",

00:22:23.762 --> 00:22:25.062
sepse nese thua "jo"

00:22:25.062 --> 00:22:27.362
kjo do te thote te shkosh ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:22:27.862 --> 00:22:32.462
Fuqia e Vishnumaya nuk do e toleroje "Jo-ne" tuaj

00:22:32.462 --> 00:22:33.762
per asgje.

00:22:33.762 --> 00:22:37.162
Shume njerez qe e kane zakon te thone, "Jo, Nene."

00:22:38.162 --> 00:22:39.362
Nuk duhet bere,

00:22:39.362 --> 00:22:43.462
sepse me tu kapur Vishuddhi juaj i majte

00:22:43.862 --> 00:22:46.362
gjithe cakrat tuaja te majta behen te dobeta,

00:22:46.362 --> 00:22:50.362
per shkak se dliresia qe eshte baza e te gjitha cakrave

00:22:51.162 --> 00:22:52.762
eshte e dobet.

00:22:53.562 --> 00:22:55.462
Ja pra sa e rendesishme eshte

00:22:55.762 --> 00:23:01.362
te kuptosh vleren e Vishuddhit te majte.

00:23:02.162 --> 00:23:03.662
Te gjithe ne te kapur ne Vishuddhin e majte,

00:23:03.862 --> 00:23:07.762
dhe nuk mendojme se eshte ndonje gje aq e rendesishme.

00:23:07.762 --> 00:23:09.362
Por ne themi, "Oh, Vishuddhi i majte po kap

00:23:09.362 --> 00:23:10.462
do te thote qe ndihem fajtor."

00:23:10.462 --> 00:23:13.562
Ne nuk e kuptojme si "Cfare kam bere?

00:23:13.562 --> 00:23:16.762
Kam kaluar kufijte, prandaj po shfaqet ketu.

00:23:18.362 --> 00:23:21.262
Kam neglizhuar ndonje lloj morali.

00:23:21.562 --> 00:23:24.862
Kam shkuar ne rrugen e gabuar kunder Nenes

00:23:25.162 --> 00:23:28.662
dhe Babait, prandaj po me kap Vishuddhi i majte."

00:23:28.662 --> 00:23:33.362
Vishuddhi i majte eshte treguesi i gabimeve,

00:23:33.862 --> 00:23:36.362
te keqijave, i mekateve.

00:23:36.662 --> 00:23:38.962
Ne s'mund ta lejojme qe te kemi Vishuddhin e majte,

00:23:39.362 --> 00:23:42.262
Sahaja yogis s'mund te perballojne te kene Vishuddhin e majte.

00:23:42.562 --> 00:23:45.162
Si shqetesime shtese, ata pijne duhan,

00:23:45.562 --> 00:23:47.162
marrin gjithe llojet te gjerave.

00:23:48.162 --> 00:23:53.062
Ne Indi ata marrin ate qe ju e quani tamakhu,

00:23:53.362 --> 00:23:57.662
eshte nje lloj- cfare gjethesh jane keto? gjethe duhani,

00:23:58.062 --> 00:24:02.462
dhe mendojne se nuk kane gabuar.

00:24:02.762 --> 00:24:04.762
Por i kap Vishuddhi i majte.

00:24:05.062 --> 00:24:08.962
Ne nje fare menyre Vishuddhi i majte eshte kyci (porta)

00:24:09.362 --> 00:24:13.162
i te gjitha llojeve te problemeve per veten tuaj,

00:24:13.662 --> 00:24:17.462
ndaj jini te kujdesshem te mos ndiheni fajtore per asgje.

00:24:18.762 --> 00:24:21.462
Me shume se kjo eshte shume vicioze, rreth vicioz i madh.

00:24:21.662 --> 00:24:24.362
Per shembull, dikush ka bere dicka te keqe.

00:24:25.562 --> 00:24:30.162
Kam vendosur t'ua them atyre ne fytyre

00:24:30.162 --> 00:24:32.562
i pelqefte ose jo, kjo eshte gabim,

00:24:32.762 --> 00:24:34.662
me shume mundesi. Sigurisht,

00:24:34.662 --> 00:24:38.162
ndonjehere perpiqem te luaj ndonje truk me ta qe ta kuptojne,

00:24:38.462 --> 00:24:41.662
nese ata s'e kuptojne te thenen Time atehere - vijme ne nje pike.

00:24:42.162 --> 00:24:45.662
Dhe une them qe "Tani me mire dilni jashte.

00:24:45.662 --> 00:24:47.862
S'mund t'ju kem ne trupin Tim me shume."

00:24:48.162 --> 00:24:49.862
Pra i nxjerr ata jashte Sahaja Yoges.

00:24:49.862 --> 00:24:51.362
Me t'i nxjerre ata nga Sahaja Yoga te pakten

00:24:51.662 --> 00:24:52.962
mbaron dhimbja Ime e kokes.

00:24:54.062 --> 00:24:55.962
Tani kam pare qe

00:24:56.162 --> 00:25:01.262
kur fillon te veproje ky negativitet, njerezit,

00:25:01.762 --> 00:25:05.162
ne vend qe te perballojne gabimet qe "Une jam gabim,

00:25:05.162 --> 00:25:07.762
nuk duhet ta kisha bere kete, eshte gje e keqe per tu bere,"

00:25:08.062 --> 00:25:10.062
fillojne japin shpjegime.

00:25:10.362 --> 00:25:11.762
Kur ju filloni te jepni shpjegime,

00:25:12.062 --> 00:25:18.762
ky Vishuddhi i majte fillon te behet si nje gunge e madhe e fryre,

00:25:19.362 --> 00:25:22.162
dhe atehere nuk ka me mundesi te sherimit,

00:25:22.162 --> 00:25:24.362
s'ka mundesi te pastrimit.

00:25:24.662 --> 00:25:26.362
Pra njerezit fillojne japin shpjegime,

00:25:26.662 --> 00:25:28.762
"Pse e bera kete, pse e bera ate."

00:25:28.962 --> 00:25:31.462
Kur thuhet eshte gabim, eshte gabim;

00:25:31.862 --> 00:25:32.762
Duhet te pranohet,

00:25:32.962 --> 00:25:34.762
"Mire, heres tjeter nuk do ta bej,

00:25:34.962 --> 00:25:36.862
Me vjen shume keq." Por "me fal"

00:25:36.862 --> 00:25:40.862
duket nje fjale shume e veshtire, te pakten

00:25:41.762 --> 00:25:42.862
per Sahaja yogistet Perendimore

00:25:42.862 --> 00:25:45.362
por gjithashtu edhe per disa Sahaja yogiste indiane,

00:25:45.362 --> 00:25:47.762
te thone, "Me fal,Me vjen shume keq."

00:25:48.162 --> 00:25:51.062
Indianet kurre s'ndihen fajtore, eshte ide e mire,

00:25:51.362 --> 00:25:56.362
por ata kurre nuk thone me fal, pra eshte njesoj.

00:26:00.662 --> 00:26:02.662
Tani dikush duhet te kuptoje

00:26:02.662 --> 00:26:05.062
qe kur ju keni kryer nje gabim,

00:26:05.262 --> 00:26:07.862
ju jeni nje qenie njerezore: te gabosh eshte njerezore

00:26:08.162 --> 00:26:09.762
dhe te falesh, hyjnore.

00:26:10.162 --> 00:26:12.262
Por duhet te dini qe keni gabuar.

00:26:12.662 --> 00:26:16.162
Nese vazhdoni te jepni shpjegime atehere nje gje eshte caktuar,

00:26:16.162 --> 00:26:18.862
ju s'kuptoni qe Zoti di gjithcka.

00:26:21.162 --> 00:26:24.262
Nese Ai thote ju keni vepruar gabim, atehere eshte gabim.

00:26:25.762 --> 00:26:27.462
Si mund te sfidosh, si mund te thuash,

00:26:27.762 --> 00:26:29.562
"E bera per kete arsye. Kjo eshte arsyeja"

00:26:29.562 --> 00:26:31.762
- kete gje duhet te kuptojme.

00:26:32.262 --> 00:26:34.362
Sepse kjo eshte fuqia e elektricitetit,

00:26:34.362 --> 00:26:36.562
duhet ta kuptoni, ju trondit.

00:26:37.262 --> 00:26:39.062
Ju godet.

00:26:39.662 --> 00:26:42.662
Dhe me pas ju kuptoni qe "Kam bere nje gabim."

00:26:42.662 --> 00:26:45.662
Keshtu qe mos krijoni tronditje per veten tuaj.

00:26:46.262 --> 00:26:47.762
Mos u sillni ne menyre

00:26:47.762 --> 00:26:50.762
qe ne fund te fundit te perfundoje me tronditje (goditje).

00:26:51.262 --> 00:26:54.262
Sigurisht, forca e Nenes eshte kaq falese,

00:26:54.762 --> 00:26:57.762
Forca e Sadashiva-s eshte kaq falese se ju jeni te lejuar,

00:26:57.762 --> 00:26:59.762
te lejuar dhe te lejuar

00:27:00.062 --> 00:27:03.662
per te vazhduar me ate qe po beni, per nje kohe.

00:27:03.862 --> 00:27:06.362
Por eshte thene,

00:27:06.362 --> 00:27:08.762
ju eshte shpjeguar qe eshte gabim.

00:27:09.162 --> 00:27:13.362
Supozojme qe kaperceni limitet tuaja absolutisht,

00:27:13.662 --> 00:27:16.262
pastaj papritur shfaqet Vishnumaya

00:27:16.262 --> 00:27:18.562
dhe e gjithe gjeja ekspozohet.

00:27:19.762 --> 00:27:22.062
Ne Sahaja Yoga ju ekspozoheni.

00:27:24.662 --> 00:27:29.662
Pra duhet te dini se edhe pse ky pushtet eshte kaq i dobishem,

00:27:30.162 --> 00:27:38.062
kaq udhezues, kaq permiresues, ushqyes dhe mbrojtes,

00:27:38.362 --> 00:27:41.062
prape - deri ne nje pike.

00:27:41.262 --> 00:27:44.362
Perndryshe Ajo vetem ju ekspozon ju,

00:27:47.762 --> 00:27:52.162
sepse Ajo s'mund te duroje me shume kete absurditet prej jush.

00:27:53.862 --> 00:27:55.362
Pra nese vazhdoni keshtu,

00:27:55.362 --> 00:27:57.462
Ajo vetem do te shohe qe Ajo eshte e ekspozuar.

00:27:57.762 --> 00:27:59.162
Keni pare njerez qe kane kryer

00:27:59.162 --> 00:28:00.562
gjithe llojet e gjerave te papastra.

00:28:00.562 --> 00:28:02.962
Kam njohur shume kryeministra

00:28:03.262 --> 00:28:05.962
e gjithe ata presidente e keta e ata,

00:28:05.962 --> 00:28:08.762
kur vdesin - ekspozohen.

00:28:14.262 --> 00:28:17.762
Askush nuk thote qe ky e ai person ishte nje person i dliret.

00:28:18.662 --> 00:28:22.662
Shume pak lidere kombesh e kane marre kete certifikate

00:28:22.962 --> 00:28:25.062
qe ishin njerez shume shume te dliret.

00:28:25.462 --> 00:28:28.762
Dliresia eshte nje certifikate shume shume e rralle qe marrin.

00:28:28.962 --> 00:28:32.962
Sepse kur ne jete merrni nje fuqi

00:28:33.762 --> 00:28:36.262
mendoni se keni dore te lire,

00:28:36.562 --> 00:28:38.962
mund te jeni e te beni cfare t'ju pelqeje.

00:28:39.262 --> 00:28:41.762
Mund te jeni nje person i dliret,

00:28:41.962 --> 00:28:44.662
mund te jeni sidoqofte i padliret,

00:28:44.962 --> 00:28:46.162
mund te beni c'tju pelqeje.

00:28:46.562 --> 00:28:50.662
Ju beheni nje lloj mbizoteruesi me kete ide qe

00:28:50.662 --> 00:28:54.362
"I kam te gjitha fuqite, tani jam vertet i mire vendosur (pozicionuar)."

00:28:54.662 --> 00:29:00.162
Dhe kjo shnderrohet ne nje zhgenjim te plote ndaj jush,

00:29:00.462 --> 00:29:03.162
dhe harroni qe dliresia eshte kaq e rendesishme.

00:29:03.162 --> 00:29:06.162
Pra sa me lart te jete nje njeri ne jete,

00:29:06.462 --> 00:29:08.362
te zere pozicion me te larte,

00:29:08.662 --> 00:29:17.862
me e larte behet ajo qe e quani ego- merr perkedhelje,

00:29:18.162 --> 00:29:22.362
me shume e shtyn poshte ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:29:22.762 --> 00:29:25.862
Pra nje person i tille arratiset ne Vishuddhin e majte,

00:29:26.162 --> 00:29:28.562
sepse thelle ne zemer,

00:29:28.562 --> 00:29:30.762
ne ndergjegjen e tij ai ndihet fajtor.

00:29:31.062 --> 00:29:34.762
Dhe e gjitha vazhdon si nje faj,

00:29:35.362 --> 00:29:37.162
faj ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:29:37.562 --> 00:29:40.762
Dhe kur shkon si faj ne Vishuddhin e majte

00:29:41.162 --> 00:29:42.762
behet nje situate e veshtire,

00:29:42.962 --> 00:29:44.362
sepse nje person i tille,

00:29:44.762 --> 00:29:46.562
behet ekstremisht i ndjeshem.

00:29:46.762 --> 00:29:49.462
Nje gje ti thuash dhe ai do te ndihet fajtor.

00:29:49.962 --> 00:29:52.562
Ti perpiqesh te kurosh Vishuddhin e tij te majte,

00:29:52.562 --> 00:29:54.862
pastaj ai behet edhe me keq.

00:29:55.362 --> 00:29:58.262
Eshte nje situate shume e keqe me njerezit e Vishuddhit te majte,

00:29:58.562 --> 00:30:01.962
dhe ka njerez qe jane te Vishuddhit te majte te cilet

00:30:02.262 --> 00:30:03.662
japin gjithmone shpjegime.

00:30:04.762 --> 00:30:07.462
Nje person qe ka Vishuddhin e djathte do jete arrogant,

00:30:07.762 --> 00:30:10.962
njerezit e Vishuddhit te majte kane nje metode shume dinake

00:30:10.962 --> 00:30:15.162
te kthimit te pergjigjes dhe shpjegimeve per cdo gje.

00:30:15.162 --> 00:30:16.262
Cfaredo te thoni, ata do te thone,

00:30:16.262 --> 00:30:18.362
"Jo Nene, kjo eshte keshtu, kjo eshte keshtu."

00:30:18.362 --> 00:30:22.062
Kjo eshte nje gje. Jo vetem kjo, s'mbaron ketu,

00:30:22.362 --> 00:30:24.062
ju jep sarkazem.

00:30:24.762 --> 00:30:28.262
Kjo eshte arsyeja pse njerezit ne Perendim nuk flasin hapur,

00:30:28.262 --> 00:30:29.862
gjithmone jane sarkastike.

00:30:30.462 --> 00:30:33.062
Ata mendojne se eshte budallallek te flasesh hapur,

00:30:33.662 --> 00:30:34.762
s'eshte inteligjente,

00:30:35.062 --> 00:30:38.362
nese dhe derisa te flasesh ne menyre shume sarkastike

00:30:38.762 --> 00:30:41.662
qe e dini ndonjehere eshte shume e veshtire per tu arritur.

00:30:44.062 --> 00:30:47.062
Kjo eshte menyra e shtrember se si ata flasin.

00:30:47.562 --> 00:30:52.362
Dhe kjo pandershmeri vjen prej ketij problemi te Vishuddhit te majte.

00:30:52.362 --> 00:30:54.262
Nese Vishuddhi i majte eshte kaq keq,

00:30:54.562 --> 00:30:59.962
nuk mund te arrini asgje qe eshte e embel,

00:31:00.462 --> 00:31:01.862
qe eshte e bukur,

00:31:03.362 --> 00:31:05.062
qe eshte e vlefshme.

00:31:06.662 --> 00:31:09.662
Vishuddhi i majte nuk do te vleresoje kurre.

00:31:10.062 --> 00:31:11.662
Ata qe vuajne nga Vishuddhi i majte

00:31:11.662 --> 00:31:14.062
s'mund ta vleresojne kurre personin tjeter, s'munden kurre.

00:31:14.762 --> 00:31:17.062
Do te kete fjalen e vet, do te mendoje, "Une jam me i miri"

00:31:17.262 --> 00:31:19.362
sepse i duhet te ekzistoje,

00:31:19.862 --> 00:31:22.262
se problemi duhet te ekzistoje, pra si?

00:31:22.262 --> 00:31:25.162
Eshte nje lloj i egos se semure

00:31:25.562 --> 00:31:26.862
qe nuk do te pranoje

00:31:26.862 --> 00:31:28.462
qe dikush mund te jete me i mire se une,

00:31:28.462 --> 00:31:30.162
qe me duhet te ndjek dike,

00:31:30.462 --> 00:31:33.162
qe me duhet te mesoj nga dikush tjeter.

00:31:33.562 --> 00:31:34.762
Kam pasur shume shembuj;

00:31:34.762 --> 00:31:36.762
E shoh sidomos tek njerezit qe jane me Mua,

00:31:36.762 --> 00:31:40.062
Gjej se ata futen ne Vishuddhin e majte shume shpejt

00:31:40.762 --> 00:31:43.662
per shkak te mungeses se protokollit.

00:31:43.662 --> 00:31:45.662
Kur fillojne te kene mungese protokolli

00:31:45.662 --> 00:31:48.062
ata shkojne ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:31:48.262 --> 00:31:50.662
Pra te jeni me Mua eshte bekim, pa dyshim,

00:31:50.862 --> 00:31:54.662
por gjithashtu duhet te jesh shume shume i kujdesshem

00:31:54.862 --> 00:31:57.462
qe te mos e kaloni protokollin.

00:31:57.762 --> 00:32:00.662
Mos u mundoni te hidheni me perpara,

00:32:01.262 --> 00:32:02.962
vetem te krekoseni.

00:32:03.562 --> 00:32:08.062
Disa njerez e kane zakon te kapercejne kufijte

00:32:08.062 --> 00:32:09.762
dhe sapo ju te kaloni kufijte

00:32:09.762 --> 00:32:11.762
krijohet Vishuddhi i majte.

00:32:12.262 --> 00:32:15.162
Nuk duhet te kete frike per Nenen tuaj,

00:32:15.362 --> 00:32:17.062
duhet te kete respekt per Nenen tuaj,

00:32:17.062 --> 00:32:20.862
gje qe ruhet nga Vishuddhi juaj i majte.

00:32:22.062 --> 00:32:26.262
Tani kjo eshte nje fuqi shume e fshehur e Shri Ganeshes.

00:32:26.562 --> 00:32:29.662
Ajo qe e quani se eshte fuqia e Ganeshes

00:32:29.662 --> 00:32:35.162
eshte Vishuddhi i majte duke vepruar si dliresia.

00:32:38.062 --> 00:32:44.562
Fuqite e Ganeshes jane shprehur te gjitha nepermjet Vishuddhit te majte.

00:32:46.362 --> 00:32:49.262
Pra ata qe besojne ne Ganesha, ne pafajsine e paster,

00:32:49.262 --> 00:32:52.062
duhet te dijne qe ne sjelljen tuaj te perditeshme,

00:32:52.362 --> 00:32:55.662
ne veprimet e perditeshme,

00:32:56.362 --> 00:32:57.862
duhet te kete dliresi.

00:32:58.162 --> 00:33:02.662
Ganesha eshte shfaqur si lulet e dliresise.

00:33:03.562 --> 00:33:07.362
Dhe vetem shihni, nese ne ligjin e hyjnores nuk ka dliresi,

00:33:07.362 --> 00:33:09.162
si i kufizoni (caktoni kufijte) njerezit,

00:33:09.162 --> 00:33:11.462
si i beni mire,

00:33:11.762 --> 00:33:13.662
si i pastroni ata,

00:33:13.962 --> 00:33:15.862
si i beni ata te evoluojne?

00:33:16.262 --> 00:33:20.662
Supozojme nje peme po rritet dhe nuk ka kufij ne te,

00:33:20.862 --> 00:33:23.262
ajo vetem rritet si nje gje e eger,

00:33:23.262 --> 00:33:24.662
nuk ka ku kufij,

00:33:24.662 --> 00:33:26.162
me pas cfare do dale nga ajo?

00:33:26.162 --> 00:33:27.362
Asgje.

00:33:27.662 --> 00:33:31.162
Pra per te bere nje person sa me te larte,

00:33:31.162 --> 00:33:32.862
duhet ta kufizoni ate (caktoni kufijte).

00:33:33.362 --> 00:33:35.962
Babai im jepte nje shembull te mire te kesaj,

00:33:35.962 --> 00:33:39.262
nese merr pak grure, fara gruri dhe
.

00:33:41.262 --> 00:33:43.262
Ne doni te dilni jashte dilni,

00:33:43.462 --> 00:33:47.062
por mos shqetesoni njerezit, duke levizur perreth.)

00:33:49.662 --> 00:33:51.562
Shikoni, edhe kjo eshte nje gje tjeter.

00:33:51.762 --> 00:33:54.562
Gjithe keto gjera s'jane asgje por

00:33:54.562 --> 00:33:56.862
turbullira te Vishuddhit te majte.

00:33:57.362 --> 00:34:02.362
Kuptoni, gjithe keto shqetesime te reklamuara

00:34:02.762 --> 00:34:05.362
ose perpjekje per mbizoterim,

00:34:05.862 --> 00:34:08.862
ose nje person shume i hedhur apo i fryre (mendjemadh)

00:34:08.862 --> 00:34:11.262
te gjitha keto vijne nga Vishuddhi i majte,

00:34:11.262 --> 00:34:13.662
sepse ju doni te kaperceni Vishuddhin tuaj te majte

00:34:13.662 --> 00:34:15.162
prandaj e beni.

00:34:16.162 --> 00:34:18.162
Me pas i shtohet edhe kjo.

00:34:18.462 --> 00:34:21.762
Sa me shume provoni ta kaperceni, aq me shume iu shtohet juve.

00:34:22.062 --> 00:34:25.362
Tani duhet t'ju tregoj historine e babait,

00:34:25.362 --> 00:34:26.862
ai tha qe nese

00:34:26.862 --> 00:34:30.962
keni grurin dhe e shperndani (hidhni pa kriter) ate,

00:34:27.749 --> 00:34:29.290
(Dikujt ne salle - Ju lutem mos me shqetesoni.

00:34:30.962 --> 00:34:33.462
ai vetem shkon kot sic ndodh me vemendjen.

00:34:34.862 --> 00:34:36.862
Por nese e vini ne nje torbe pelhure,

00:34:37.362 --> 00:34:38.362
ne nje cante,

00:34:38.862 --> 00:34:43.662
ju mund ta mblidhni grumbull (tog) dhe ai mund te arrije lartesi.

00:34:44.462 --> 00:34:45.662
Ne te njejten menyre,

00:34:45.862 --> 00:34:48.962
nese e shkon kot vemendjen tende pa dliresi,

00:34:49.162 --> 00:34:50.762
ajo shperndahet;

00:34:51.662 --> 00:34:54.662
nuk ka kufij, nuk ka forma,

00:34:54.662 --> 00:34:56.062
nuk ka trajte.

00:34:56.262 --> 00:34:57.662
Por nese ti e kufizon ate,

00:34:58.662 --> 00:35:02.862
atehere ju beheni me i larte me i larte me i larte,

00:35:03.162 --> 00:35:07.362
dhe mund te ngrihesh me lart ne jeten tende shpirterore.

00:35:07.862 --> 00:35:12.462
Meqe ju jeni njerez qe doni te keni nje jete shume shpirterore,

00:35:12.762 --> 00:35:19.662
duhet te kuptoni qe Vishuddhi i majte duhet te korrigjohet.

00:35:20.562 --> 00:35:24.562
Tani, si e korrigjoni Vishuddhin e majte?

00:35:25.462 --> 00:35:27.662
Ndonjehere lodhem shume me ta,

00:35:27.662 --> 00:35:29.862
ndihem vertet- lodhem shume,

00:35:30.162 --> 00:35:32.162
Thjesht heq dore prej tyre.

00:35:32.762 --> 00:35:34.662
Sepse nese ato po ju kapin (ngercet).

00:35:34.662 --> 00:35:36.062
dhe ju u thoni " Po me kapni"

00:35:36.362 --> 00:35:38.762
ato behen edhe me keq. C'rreth vicioz qe eshte.

00:35:39.162 --> 00:35:40.662
Cila eshte kura per kete?

00:35:40.662 --> 00:35:44.762
Si ta thyejme kete rreth vicioz?- duke e perballur ate.

00:35:45.662 --> 00:35:47.862
Duhet te themi, "Cfare, po ndihesh fajtor per cfare?

00:35:47.862 --> 00:35:49.762
Po beni te njejtin gabim perseri e perseri,

00:35:49.762 --> 00:35:51.462
dhe ende jeni duke e bere."

00:35:51.462 --> 00:35:57.162
Duhet ti beni te gjitha injeksionet vetes.

00:35:57.362 --> 00:36:00.462
Por ne vend te kesaj fillojne te Me thone,

00:36:00.762 --> 00:36:03.762
"Jo, Nene. Jo, Nene. Jo, Nene."

00:36:04.262 --> 00:36:06.962
I thoni vetes, "Jo, une vete."

00:36:07.962 --> 00:36:10.862
Sot kam bere kete, neser do te bej kete,

00:36:10.862 --> 00:36:12.262
te pasnesermen do te bej kete.

00:36:12.262 --> 00:36:16.562
Ndal tani, ndal." Dhe ndalo ne kete pike.

00:36:17.162 --> 00:36:20.562
Atje ju ushtroni fuqine e Vishnumaya.

00:36:21.062 --> 00:36:24.662
Fuqia e Vishnumaya duhet te neutralizohet,

00:36:25.862 --> 00:36:29.362
nese eshte keshtu, prej gabimeve tuaja;

00:36:29.762 --> 00:36:34.762
por nese do ti duhet tju ktheje ne fuqite e saj

00:36:35.062 --> 00:36:36.762
ju duhet te perdorni fuqite e Vishnumaya

00:36:36.762 --> 00:36:39.162
duke i dhene vetes goditje.

00:36:42.262 --> 00:36:43.862
Vetem ju mund ta beni kete.

00:36:43.862 --> 00:36:46.662
Pra ne kete pike, ne piken e Vishnumaya

00:36:46.662 --> 00:36:48.762
Une vertet deshtoj ndaj jush.

00:36:49.162 --> 00:36:50.962
Ju duhet ta beni kete.

00:36:53.062 --> 00:36:56.362
Dhe prandaj une po mendoja per kete puja

00:36:56.662 --> 00:37:00.162
qe kur ju njerez te benit kete puja ndaj Meje,

00:37:00.762 --> 00:37:05.062
nese them ndonje gje do te krijoj me shume Vishnumaya tek ju.

00:37:05.062 --> 00:37:07.762
Por kjo eshte gjeja me e lehte te menaxhosh gjerat, me kuptoni -

00:37:07.762 --> 00:37:11.962
"Po ndihem fajtor" - jeni te mbaruar.

00:37:12.362 --> 00:37:14.762
"E mora ndeshkimin, e quajta veten fajtor."

00:37:15.162 --> 00:37:19.062
Eshte si ne gjyq juria ju thote qe jeni fajtor

00:37:19.062 --> 00:37:22.462
- mire, e pranoj, "Une jam fajtor," por jo ndeshkimin,

00:37:23.762 --> 00:37:25.062
pa marre ndeshkim.

00:37:25.562 --> 00:37:28.362
Nese ke vepruar gabim, atehere ndeshkoje veten.

00:37:28.662 --> 00:37:30.362
Ka dy menyra per te ndeshkuar njerezit.

00:37:30.762 --> 00:37:33.562
Njera eshte qe disa  ndeshkohen

00:37:33.562 --> 00:37:36.462
duke thene qe "Nuk do te kem ushqim."

00:37:36.462 --> 00:37:39.562
Por ata njerez qe kane zakonin e te mos pasurit ushqim

00:37:39.562 --> 00:37:42.162
e keto gjera, mund edhe te behen agresive

00:37:42.162 --> 00:37:44.162
me kete lloj zakoni te trazojne te tjeret

00:37:44.162 --> 00:37:48.562
per te mos ngrene ushqim. Them, qeniet njerezore jane shume te pasinqerta.

00:37:49.062 --> 00:37:50.562
Dijne si ta vrasin veten

00:37:50.562 --> 00:37:52.262
me nje thike tinzare gjithe kohes.

00:37:52.662 --> 00:37:54.862
Pra nuk ka menyre si ta korrigjosh veten.

00:37:55.962 --> 00:37:58.162
Nese te duhet te korrigjosh veten,

00:37:58.562 --> 00:38:02.062
atehere duhet ta perballesh veten ne menyren e duhur.

00:38:03.562 --> 00:38:05.962
Te supozojme keni bere dicka gabim,

00:38:06.562 --> 00:38:09.662
atehere duhet te beni dicka qe

00:38:09.662 --> 00:38:11.962
do ju pelqeje ta beni normalisht,

00:38:13.362 --> 00:38:14.562
dhe te ndeshkoni veten.

00:38:14.562 --> 00:38:16.362
Ju duhet, ju duhet, me vjen keq,

00:38:16.362 --> 00:38:18.362
ju nuk duhet te beni dicka

00:38:18.362 --> 00:38:20.062
qe normalisht do ju pelqente ta benit.

00:38:20.062 --> 00:38:22.062
Ashtu si te korrigjosh veten;

00:38:22.062 --> 00:38:28.462
te themi qe dikush eshte shume i dhene ndaj lulishteve, luleve.

00:38:29.062 --> 00:38:30.362
Kur beni gabime

00:38:30.362 --> 00:38:33.162
per pak kohe nuk shihni lule,

00:38:35.162 --> 00:38:37.562
vetem mbyllni syte tuaj per lule.

00:38:38.062 --> 00:38:40.862
Ka njerez, te supozojme,

00:38:41.062 --> 00:38:45.162
qe jane te dhene pas te kenduarit,

00:38:47.062 --> 00:38:51.162
keshtu nese beni gabime direkt ndalojne se kenduarit.

00:38:55.762 --> 00:38:57.762
Keshtu ju duhet te godisni.

00:38:58.662 --> 00:39:01.862
Duhet ta dini qe Vishnumaya eshte nje rrufe,

00:39:02.162 --> 00:39:04.162
dhe leksioni duhet te jete i tille.

00:39:04.562 --> 00:39:07.762
Nuk mund te jete aq i bute, sic ishte Shri Krishna.

00:39:08.162 --> 00:39:10.562
Po ju them qe eshte nje gje shume e fuqishme,

00:39:10.862 --> 00:39:17.662
dhe mundte Zoti te zgjoje ate fuqi te brendshme te Vishnumaya

00:39:17.962 --> 00:39:21.962
Eshte gjeja me e fuqishme qe nje qenie njerezore mund te kete,

00:39:22.262 --> 00:39:23.862
eshte gjeja me fatlume;

00:39:23.862 --> 00:39:26.662
ju beheni nje personalitet i shenjte.

00:39:29.462 --> 00:39:33.262
Kjo eshte nje nga menyrat e gjetjes se realizimit te Zotit.

00:39:34.262 --> 00:39:37.362
Kjo ishte nje pyetje e bukur e pyetur me vend,

00:39:37.662 --> 00:39:39.162
tamam ne kohe dje,

00:39:39.462 --> 00:39:42.362
te stabilizoni dliresine tuaj

00:39:43.062 --> 00:39:44.662
- por jo duke dhene bandhan,

00:39:44.662 --> 00:39:47.662
duke marre vibrime nga Nena dhe me pas t'i humbisni,

00:39:47.862 --> 00:39:50.762
jo ne kete menyre: ju vete te korrigjoni veten

00:39:50.962 --> 00:39:52.662
nga mengjesi ne darke,

00:39:53.662 --> 00:39:56.762
dhe te perballni veten pa u ndjere fajtore,

00:39:58.362 --> 00:40:00.362
dhe te mesoni gjera te reja.

00:40:00.962 --> 00:40:04.362
Gjithe kohes eshte motra qe ju meson,

00:40:04.362 --> 00:40:07.662
gjithe kohes, si te jeni me mire dhe me mire dhe me mire,

00:40:07.662 --> 00:40:08.862
jo Nena;

00:40:09.162 --> 00:40:11.062
sepse Nenes mund ti thoni, "Jo, Nene."

00:40:11.062 --> 00:40:14.362
Nese i thoni nje motre - elektricitet,

00:40:14.662 --> 00:40:15.862
ne rregull?

00:40:16.362 --> 00:40:20.162
Futini gishtat ne prize dhe do te kuptoni

00:40:21.162 --> 00:40:23.262
- pa shpjegime!

00:40:31.162 --> 00:40:33.062
Me kete mirekuptim,

00:40:35.462 --> 00:40:38.162
per stabilizimin e dliresise suaj,

00:40:38.462 --> 00:40:43.462
dliresi te emocioneve tona dhe dliresi te mendjes sone.

00:40:44.162 --> 00:40:45.762
Cfaredo te keni bere deri tani,

00:40:45.762 --> 00:40:47.562
harrojeni, harrojeni te shkuaren.

00:40:47.762 --> 00:40:50.762
Kjo eshte shume e rendesishme gjithashtu, te harrosh te shkuaren,

00:40:50.962 --> 00:40:52.962
sepse kuptoni qe eshte nje menyre shume e mire e te shpjeguarit,

00:40:52.962 --> 00:40:55.462
"Ngaqe pata kete, prandaj me ndodhi.

00:40:55.462 --> 00:40:58.162
Nena ime ishte keshtu, edhe babai im ishte keshtu

00:40:58.562 --> 00:41:01.562
"Nene, baba, harroni gjithkend tani,

00:41:01.562 --> 00:41:04.662
ju i perkisni kesaj familje, qe eshte nje familje e shenjte.

00:41:05.162 --> 00:41:08.562
Njerezit qe jane shenjtore

00:41:09.962 --> 00:41:13.362
ndodhen te ulur ketu, ju jeni midis tyre.

00:41:14.162 --> 00:41:17.862
Dhe automatikisht keto ligje do fillojne te punojne,

00:41:17.862 --> 00:41:19.662
dhe nuk do na duhet t'ju themi

00:41:19.862 --> 00:41:21.562
nese duhet te jeni miqesor me kete person

00:41:21.123 --> 00:41:23.499
ne do te bejme sot puja

00:41:21.562 --> 00:41:24.162
ose jo miqesor me ate person.

00:41:26.662 --> 00:41:29.662
Shikoni, interesimi ne seksin e kunder

00:41:30.062 --> 00:41:34.362
gjithe kohes nuk eshte shenje e dliresise.

00:41:35.762 --> 00:41:40.062
Dua te them, eshte i frikshem, absolutisht qesharak,

00:41:40.362 --> 00:41:42.162
ju beheni budalla.

00:41:42.762 --> 00:41:45.662
Si disa burra qe dine kaq shume gjera grash,

00:41:45.862 --> 00:41:47.762
parfume, kjo, ajo. C'dobi kane?

00:41:47.762 --> 00:41:50.262
Jeni skllever te grave, apo cfare?

00:41:50.762 --> 00:41:53.562
Ata behen eksperte ne gjera te paarsyeshme (pakuptimta).

00:41:55.362 --> 00:41:57.462
Ju jeni burra, jetoni si burra.

00:41:59.562 --> 00:42:02.762
Dhe grate duhet te kene ate ndjenje dliresie

00:42:02.762 --> 00:42:05.462
brenda vetes tyre, sepse ato jane forcat (fuqite).

00:42:06.362 --> 00:42:09.162
Pse doni te beheni si burrat?

00:42:09.562 --> 00:42:11.662
Dua te them, ju jeni fuqia prapa tyre.

00:42:13.162 --> 00:42:15.862
Dhe grate duhet te kujdesen per dliresine e tyre.

00:42:16.262 --> 00:42:18.062
Per kete duhet te them,

00:42:18.862 --> 00:42:23.162
duhet t'i perulem grave Indiane,

00:42:24.662 --> 00:42:25.962
menyra si jane te perulura,

00:42:26.562 --> 00:42:28.062
menyra si jane te dlira,

00:42:28.062 --> 00:42:30.362
ju duhet te mesoni- sigurisht ka shume

00:42:30.362 --> 00:42:33.762
edhe shume qe s'jane te tilla- por perulja qe ato kane.

00:42:35.562 --> 00:42:40.762
Ka vetem nje kategori qe nuk duhet te kete perulje:

00:42:42.162 --> 00:42:45.862
qe eshte misherimet.

00:42:46.762 --> 00:42:50.562
Une s'mund te kem perulesi, keq ta them.

00:42:50.962 --> 00:42:52.862
Ka cilesi te caktuar qe ju keni

00:42:52.862 --> 00:42:54.762
dhe i gezoni e mbani, une s'mund ti kem.

00:42:54.962 --> 00:43:00.762
Une nuk mund te perul Veten Time, s'mund ta bej, Me vjen keq

00:43:03.162 --> 00:43:05.162
- Une nuk duhet ta bej kete.

00:43:05.962 --> 00:43:08.362
Asnje misherim s'ishte i perulur;

00:43:08.662 --> 00:43:10.062
ata s'munden,

00:43:11.362 --> 00:43:13.962
sepse ata nuk kane asnje faj.

00:43:20.762 --> 00:43:24.162
Kam vene kaq shume njerez fajtore ne Vishudhin Tim te majte

00:43:24.562 --> 00:43:28.362
saqe veshet e Mi po bllokohen duke u perpjekur te pastrohen.

00:43:28.562 --> 00:43:30.162
Nese mund te pastroni fajin tuaj

00:43:30.462 --> 00:43:33.662
veshet e Mi do te hapen, shqetesimi Im do te largohet.

00:43:33.662 --> 00:43:35.062
Ndaj ju lutem, ju kerkoj qe

00:43:35.362 --> 00:43:37.462
te mbani mire Vishuddhin tuaj te majte.

00:43:37.462 --> 00:43:40.362
Mos u ndjeni fajtor, jini ne qender.

00:43:41.062 --> 00:43:44.362
Jini ne qender, vezhgoni veten dhe perballuni me te,

00:43:44.562 --> 00:43:46.462
goditeni veten, korrigjojeni veten.

00:43:46.462 --> 00:43:49.662
Vetem njerez te tille do te ngjiten.

00:43:51.262 --> 00:43:53.962
Nje rruge tjeter eshte meditimi.

00:43:54.362 --> 00:43:56.062
Me doren e majte drejt fotografise,

00:43:56.062 --> 00:43:58.962
me driten atje, dora e djathte ne Nenen Toke,

00:43:59.762 --> 00:44:00.862
mund t'ia dilni.

00:44:00.862 --> 00:44:02.362
Vendoseni driten ketu lart,

00:44:02.362 --> 00:44:04.162
jepini nje bandhan Vishuddhit tuaj te majte,

00:44:04.162 --> 00:44:05.162
mund t'ia dilni.

00:44:05.162 --> 00:44:08.862
Por keto mund te behen rituale nese nuk i beni me zemer.

00:44:09.162 --> 00:44:12.862
Pra para se gjithash perballuni me te, menderisht perballuni me te plotesisht,

00:44:12.862 --> 00:44:14.562
me pas bejeni me keto gjera.

00:44:14.562 --> 00:44:16.662
Kuptojeni edhe emocionalisht,

00:44:16.962 --> 00:44:21.162
qe emocionet qe ju keni nuk duhet te kene faj ne to.

00:44:23.062 --> 00:44:25.162
Pra per te gjitha qellimet tona praktike

00:44:25.462 --> 00:44:29.762
ne s'do te perdorim gjithe keto fjale te cilat tregojne fajin tone

00:44:30.062 --> 00:44:31.162
- por peruljen.

00:44:31.662 --> 00:44:34.962
Perulja eshte shume e ndryshme nga nje person fajtor.

00:44:35.162 --> 00:44:39.062
Personi fajtor eshte personi qe eshte nen presion,

00:44:39.362 --> 00:44:43.362
nen presion, por nje njeri i perulur eshte nje person i lire.

00:44:44.362 --> 00:44:48.262
Eshte i perulur ne vete lirine e tij, ne vete euforine e tij.

00:44:48.362 --> 00:44:50.662
Si pemet, kur ato jane te ngarkuara me fruta

00:44:50.662 --> 00:44:54.562
ato thjesht i perulen Nenes Toke.

00:44:55.562 --> 00:44:58.162
Njelloj, nese shkoni ne det,

00:44:58.162 --> 00:45:02.462
do shihni qe gjithe pemet rreth detit,

00:45:02.762 --> 00:45:05.462
vecanerisht pemet e kokosit,

00:45:05.462 --> 00:45:08.062
te gjitha kthehen drejt detit

00:45:08.962 --> 00:45:11.862
sepse deti u ka dhene atyre vecanesine.

00:45:11.862 --> 00:45:15.662
Uji qe eshte ne kokos vjen nga deti.

00:45:15.662 --> 00:45:20.662
Prandaj ato te gjitha kane kete respekt,

00:45:20.962 --> 00:45:23.662
ate perulje ndaj detit.

00:45:23.962 --> 00:45:30.262
Ne te njejten menyre nje person qe nuk eshte fajtor

00:45:30.762 --> 00:45:33.462
vetem do jete i perulur realisht,

00:45:33.662 --> 00:45:35.462
sepse njerezit fajtore, sic ju kam thene,

00:45:35.662 --> 00:45:39.662
jane agresive me sarkazmen e tyre, me fjalet e ndyra,

00:45:39.662 --> 00:45:42.462
me kthimpergjigjet e tyre, me shpjegimet e tyre.

00:45:42.762 --> 00:45:49.562
Por nje person i perulur eshte nje person i lire,

00:45:49.962 --> 00:45:51.662
i lire per te qene i perulur,

00:45:52.162 --> 00:45:55.162
i lire per te qene i mire,

00:45:55.562 --> 00:45:57.762
i bute, i meshirshem.

00:45:58.062 --> 00:46:02.562
Dhe ky lloj Sahaja Yogis duhet te jeni,

00:46:02.862 --> 00:46:04.562
qe kur njerezit t'ju takojne

00:46:04.562 --> 00:46:06.162
te jene te impresionuar nga perulja juaj.

00:46:06.362 --> 00:46:10.462
Por perulesia nuk ka ndonje servilizem

00:46:10.862 --> 00:46:13.662
- pafajesi dhe perulesi.

00:46:15.362 --> 00:46:18.762
Une, mua me mungon kjo cilesi teresisht.

00:46:19.162 --> 00:46:20.562
Une s'mund te jem e perulur,

00:46:20.862 --> 00:46:23.062
dhe ju nuk duhet te perpiqeni te Me perulni,

00:46:23.062 --> 00:46:25.162
sepse kjo nuk duhet bere.

00:46:25.762 --> 00:46:31.262
Por askush s'mund te thote per sjelljen Time kur Me takojne

00:46:31.262 --> 00:46:33.162
qe nuk jam e perulur. Une veproj me perulje.

00:46:37.462 --> 00:46:41.362
Mund te veproj si njeri shume i perulur por per te qene e sinqerte,

00:46:41.662 --> 00:46:45.562
Une nuk kam asnje lloj perulesie brenda Meje, jo perulesi.

00:46:45.762 --> 00:46:49.062
Dhembshuria eshte shume ndryshe nga perulesia.

00:46:49.362 --> 00:46:52.262
Perulesia eshte nje cilesi njerezore,

00:46:52.662 --> 00:46:56.462
eshte nje cilesi e vecante qe vetem bhaktas e kane.

00:46:57.062 --> 00:47:00.662
Vetem bhaktas e kane, eshte nje cilesi kaq e bukur

00:47:01.262 --> 00:47:04.662
te marresh rreke (dushe) te lumturise.

00:47:05.662 --> 00:47:08.762
Ai qe jep lumturi s'mund te jete i perulur

00:47:08.762 --> 00:47:10.862
sepse s'mund te marre asgje.

00:47:11.062 --> 00:47:14.862
Jane vetem qeniet njerezore ato qe jane te perulura,

00:47:15.162 --> 00:47:18.662
dhe mund ta kapin, arrijne dhe ta marrin ate.

00:47:18.862 --> 00:47:24.962
Dhe personi qe s'mund ta kape ate eshte kaq i vetmuar, kaq i vetmuar.

00:47:25.462 --> 00:47:30.662
Nje person i tille s'mund te kete shoqeri me asnje,

00:47:31.062 --> 00:47:33.562
sepse i duhet te jape, te jape e te jape.

00:47:33.562 --> 00:47:40.062
Eshte kaq i vetmuar dhe i duhet te perballoje cdo gje vetem.

00:47:40.362 --> 00:47:44.062
Ata qe jane te perulur vetem mund te behen miqesore

00:47:44.062 --> 00:47:48.562
me njeri tjetrin, mund te ndajne problemet e tyre me njeri tjetrin.

00:47:48.762 --> 00:47:52.862
Une s'mundem, sepse ju nuk keni asnje zgjidhje

00:47:53.562 --> 00:47:55.762
Me duhet te zgjidh problemet e Mia.

00:47:56.062 --> 00:48:01.062
Pra perulja vetem ju ndihmon te artikuloni

00:48:01.362 --> 00:48:03.362
dhe te keni raporte me miqte tuaj,

00:48:03.662 --> 00:48:06.262
me cdokend, ndani veshtiresite tuaja.

00:48:06.662 --> 00:48:09.362
Por perseri me duhet t'ju paralajmeroj sepse ndodh gjithmone,

00:48:09.662 --> 00:48:12.862
perulesia juaj s'duhet te jete e kendshme (argetuese).

00:48:14.362 --> 00:48:16.962
Perulesia eshte nje person i shkeputur,

00:48:16.962 --> 00:48:19.162
eshte nje cilesi e shkeputur.

00:48:19.362 --> 00:48:22.262
S'eshte nje cilesi qe behet e ngjitur (varur)

00:48:22.262 --> 00:48:24.262
per nje person apo personi te dyte.

00:48:25.062 --> 00:48:27.162
Eshte nje stil i perulur jetese

00:48:27.162 --> 00:48:29.462
ku ju nuk jeni arrogant pa qene nevoja,

00:48:29.762 --> 00:48:31.462
nuk u bertisni njerezve.

00:48:31.762 --> 00:48:35.362
Por ne Indi ne themi lopa

00:48:35.762 --> 00:48:37.362
eshte nje kafshe shume e perulur.

00:48:37.662 --> 00:48:39.362
Jep qumeshtin e saj,

00:48:40.162 --> 00:48:42.162
siguron gjithcka,

00:48:42.362 --> 00:48:44.262
nuk sulmon asnje.

00:48:46.162 --> 00:48:49.362
Pra perulja eshte nje roje e tille per ju.

00:48:50.062 --> 00:48:52.562
Sigurisht, ndonjehere njerezit perfitojne nga njerezit e perulur,

00:48:52.762 --> 00:48:53.362
s'ka problem.

00:48:53.362 --> 00:48:55.962
Per sa kohe qe nuk e keni humbur perulesine tuaj,

00:48:56.262 --> 00:48:57.162
cdo gje eshte ne rregull.

00:48:57.462 --> 00:48:58.962
Por njerezit e humbin perulesine e tyre.

00:48:58.962 --> 00:49:00.462
Kur disa perpiqen ti shqetesojne ata

00:49:00.462 --> 00:49:01.962
ata behen Vishuddhe te majte

00:49:01.962 --> 00:49:05.162
dhe pastaj e humbin perulesine e tyre,

00:49:05.562 --> 00:49:07.662
dhe kjo eshte nje gje qe s'duhet humbur;

00:49:08.162 --> 00:49:12.062
sepse nese te duhet te mbash lidhjen me Hyjnoren

00:49:12.362 --> 00:49:14.662
duhet te jesh i perulur,

00:49:14.962 --> 00:49:16.662
S'ka rruge tjeter.

00:49:17.162 --> 00:49:19.362
Nese nuk je nje person i perulur

00:49:19.862 --> 00:49:21.662
s'mund te mbash marredhenie.

00:49:21.962 --> 00:49:25.762
Kuptoni, dy cilesite, si spina dhe priza.

00:49:26.062 --> 00:49:27.962
Spina duhet te jete spine,

00:49:28.162 --> 00:49:30.262
priza duhet te jete prize.

00:49:30.262 --> 00:49:32.262
Njelloj nese duhet te

00:49:32.562 --> 00:49:35.162
merrni dicka prej Hyjnores,

00:49:35.162 --> 00:49:36.962
duhet te jeni person i perulur.

00:49:36.962 --> 00:49:39.962
Nepermjet arrogances s'mund te merrni asgje,

00:49:40.362 --> 00:49:43.162
nepermjet agresionit s'mund te merrni asgje,

00:49:43.762 --> 00:49:46.062
nepermjet asgjeje. Dhe disa njerez mund te ndjejne qe

00:49:46.062 --> 00:49:49.462
"E dua Nenen," por kjo dashuri duhet te shprehet

00:49:49.662 --> 00:49:51.662
nepermjet perulesise se plote.

00:49:53.762 --> 00:49:55.662
Kjo eshte e vetmja menyre,

00:49:55.962 --> 00:49:59.862
ky eshte i vetmi kanal nepermjet te cilit ju mund te Me afroheni,

00:50:00.162 --> 00:50:01.962
s'ka rrugedalje.

00:50:03.562 --> 00:50:11.462
Pra e mbyllim sot ne nje faze shume te larte.

00:50:12.662 --> 00:50:15.162
Eshte fillimi i realizimit te Zotit.

00:50:15.562 --> 00:50:17.662
Por duhet te shpejtoni me Mua.

00:50:18.062 --> 00:50:20.162
Nuk eshte e lehte te mbani shpejtesine me Mua,

00:50:20.562 --> 00:50:22.362
pra ju duhet te shpejtoni me Mua.

00:50:22.362 --> 00:50:24.562
Nese duhet te shkoni drejt realizimit te Zotit,

00:50:24.862 --> 00:50:30.562
fillimisht stabilizoni sensin tuaj te dliresise dhe perulesise.

00:50:33.662 --> 00:50:36.762
Zoti ju bekofte.

